  <name>OpenRA - Sole Survivor</name>
  <summary>An open-source remake of the original Sole Survivor game</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      OpenRA Sole Survivor is a project that recreates and modernizes the Sole Survivor real time strategy game, using the open-source OpenRA game engine. 
    </p>
    <p>
      OpenRA Sole Survivor is free in itself, but it requires assets from the original Sole Survivor game, which are not free. 
    </p>
